<div
  style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0px auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 20px 50px; font-family: arial;">
  <table style="width: 100%;">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td style="background-color: rgb(94, 94, 94); text-align: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"><img
            src="https://terminal-files.ecom.com/static/img/emailers/logo-white.png" style="width: 200px; padding: 20px;"></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <div style="padding: 60px 70px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);">
    <div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 16px;">Hi <%= name %>,</div>
    <div style="font-size: 16px;">
      <p>The system has detected that your account is logged in from a new IP address or a new Device. This will happen if you have a dynamic IP address, which is common.</p>
      <div style="color: #636363; background-color: #f2f6f8 ; padding: 20px; font-size: 14px;font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;
      font-family: 'Lato', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
        <div>IP          : &nbsp;&nbsp;<%= ip %></div>
        <br>
        <div>Time        : &nbsp;&nbsp;<%= time %></div>
        <br>
        <div>Device      : &nbsp;&nbsp;<%= device %></div>
        <br>
        <div>Location      : &nbsp;&nbsp;<%= location %></div>
      </div>
      <p>Confirm the login, please click the button below:</p>
      <a href="<%= resetHref %>"
        style="padding: 8px 20px; background-color: #3581d6; color: #fff; font-weight: bolder; font-size: 17px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0px; margin-right: 20px; text-decoration: none;  font-family: 'Lato', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">CONFIRM
        LOGIN</a>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 5% 0px;">
      <h4 style="margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: left;">Need Help?</h4>
      <div
        style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; text-align: left;">
        <span
          style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">If
          this wasn't you, we recommend you suspend&nbsp;your account</span><span
          style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;immediately
          and contact&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:support@ecom.com" target="_blank"
          style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">support@ecom.com</a><span
          style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;to
          report this incident.</span></div>
      <div
        style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">
        <div style="font-size: 16px; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; text-align: left;">For any other queries, reply directly to this email.</div>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; text-align: left;">Sincerely,</div>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; text-align: left;">The ecom Team</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div style="text-align: center; background: rgb(242, 244, 248); padding: 8px; margin-top: 32px;">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/ecom.exchange/" target="_blank"
        style="display: inline-block; margin: 0px 10px; color: rgb(62, 75, 90);"><img
          src="https://terminal-files.ecom.com/static/img/emailers/facebook-logo.png" style="width: 20px;"></a><a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/ecom/" target="_blank"
        style="display: inline-block; margin: 0px 10px; color: rgb(62, 75, 90);"><img
          src="https://terminal-files.ecom.com/static/img/emailers/linkedin-logo.png" style="width: 20px;"></a><a
        href="https://twitter.com/ecom" target="_blank"
        style="display: inline-block; margin: 0px 10px; color: rgb(62, 75, 90);"><img
          src="https://terminal-files.ecom.com/static/img/emailers/twitter-logo.png" style="width: 20px;"></a><a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/ecom.exchange/" target="_blank"
        style="display: inline-block; margin: 0px 10px; color: rgb(62, 75, 90);"><img
          src="https://terminal-files.ecom.com/static/img/emailers/instagram.png" style="width: 20px;"></a></div><strong><span
        style="font-size: 12px;"><a href="https://support.ecom.com/" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(62, 75, 90);">Help
          Centre</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="mailto:hello@ecom.com" target="_blank"
          style="color: rgb(62, 75, 90);">Contact Us</a></span></strong>
  </div>
